c: 9
v: 19
t: "Nicinga ukuba ukubonelela abahambi abangcwele ngamanzi okusela nokugcina iMasjid eNgcwele (eMakkah) kuyafana na ngexabiso nabo bakholwa kuAllâh nakwiMini yokuGqibela, bezabalaza ngamandla besilwa eNdleleni ka-Allâh? Abafani phambi koAllâh. Kananjalo uAllâh Akabakhokeli abantu abangabagabadeli"